{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-5e6f-4a7b-8c9d-0e1f2a3b4c5d",
    "name": "Solanium · API completa",
    "description": "Colección end-to-end para validar todas las APIs del backend Solanium en una sola corrida del Collection Runner.\n\n**Pre-requisitos**\n1. Backend corriendo en `http://localhost:4000` (`cd backend && npm run dev`).\n2. Migraciones aplicadas (`npm run migrate`) y seed cargado (`npm run seed:test`).\n3. Selecciona el environment `Solanium · Local`.\n\n**Cómo correr**\n- Click en `Run collection` → ejecuta los folders en orden (Setup → Reads → CRUD → Super-admin → Cleanup).\n- Cada request guarda automáticamente IDs y tokens en variables de colección, así que no hay que tocar nada.\n- El folder Cleanup elimina los recursos creados durante la corrida; ejecutarla repetidamente es seguro.\n\nVer `docs/postman/README.md` para detalles.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      { "key": "token", "value": "{{session_token}}", "type": "string" }
    ]
  },
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "// Pre-request global: garantiza que las variables dinámicas existen.",
          "if (!pm.collectionVariables.get('run_stamp')) {",
          "  pm.collectionVariables.set('run_stamp', String(Date.now()));",
          "}"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "listen": "test",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "// Aserción global: ningún request debe responder 5xx.",
          "pm.test('No 5xx server error', function () {",
          "  pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.be.below(500);",
          "});"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "variable": [
    { "key": "run_stamp", "value": "" },
    { "key": "session_token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "tenant_id", "value": "" },
    { "key": "activation_id", "value": "" },
    { "key": "current_code", "value": "" },
    { "key": "logged_user_id", "value": "" },
    { "key": "created_user_id", "value": "" },
    { "key": "customer_id", "value": "" },
    { "key": "product_id", "value": "" },
    { "key": "template_id", "value": "" },
    { "key": "invoice_id", "value": "" },
    { "key": "new_tenant_id", "value": "" },
    { "key": "new_tenant_slug", "value": "" },
    { "key": "new_activation_id", "value": "" },
